{"tid":1728830,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］樓下間酒樓專做支那生意，點整走佢好？","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T00:51:47.000Z","uid":23968,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8a6939a71c8cab3358039e844393692c71b63c","tid":1728830,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:41:05.000Z","msg":"明明民區，但就開黎淨做支那遊客生意，攪到區內污煙漳氣<br />\n可以點玩死間野？"},{"pid":"4097029913fa293423c19547043ad9af2d8df3a5","tid":1728830,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"如果強国人知道食物中毒有錢賠"},{"pid":"bc954b804765dd5da16841efa31d30d57d4b903a","tid":1728830,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"間野幾年黎都係咁 好想整死佢"},{"pid":"f8dc5f3fafc9bb471312ed6e396c160361f3edc6","tid":1728830,"uid":103668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"放鼠"},{"pid":"60d6b9880572de79ded8609455c9bbd0f48d20dc","tid":1728830,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"他們在打的是「<strong>中共政權保衛戰</strong>」，而你們僅僅是在打「<strong>香港生活方式保衛戰</strong>」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，第一就是分化，把勇武派、和理非派拆分，第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"0c9748d2906aa88dc9e0efa09b297b4e8cb215a9","tid":1728830,"uid":130594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:57:25.000Z","msg":"褲能正仆佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919504642fd1fb0a23899915c6e645547dba285a","tid":1728830,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f8dc5f3fafc9bb471312ed6e396c160361f3edc6","tid":1728830,"uid":103668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"放鼠"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"有無合法攪9佢既方法？<br />\n例如酒樓會好易違規咩野 日日去1823 投訴咁？"},{"pid":"c43eb852c6a5cbdf270ec78cbc4e4f98329ac991","tid":1728830,"uid":171604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"留名學野先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035952681df068d3defa862ce55dc516f171c57d","tid":1728830,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"919504642fd1fb0a23899915c6e645547dba285a","tid":1728830,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f8dc5f3fafc9bb471312ed6e396c160361f3edc6","tid":1728830,"uid":103668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:51:46.000Z","msg":"放鼠"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"有無合法攪9佢既方法？<br />\n例如酒樓會好易違規咩野 日日去1823 投訴咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"消防、食環一定中"},{"pid":"2e40da3179edae8ec5bf07552d06eb17c0fb3d23","tid":1728830,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"邊區先"},{"pid":"4290e0ce1dcbf82af33355655c2655913eafc5c0","tid":1728830,"uid":117276,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"裝修"},{"pid":"fb85da0d0aa995f6c8f8f0744